svg.text: Eternity's health report is designed to help identify early signs of potential health risks. These assessments do not look for all
diseases or healths conditions. Eternity's health report assessment results should be evaluated in addition to the results of other
tests, medical history, physical examination and other relavant information.
The information provide should not be use to diagnose or treat a health problem or disease without consulting with a qualified
health care provider, specific tests, physicians, procedures, opinions, or other qualified medical information.
Eternity's health report results within the optimum range do not mean that a disease or health condition is not present. Test
results within the high risk range do not mean that a disease or health condition is present. Test results may vary if repeated,
